{
  "stem": "7722.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's name was Haim, and my mother's name was Bina.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I knew-- I knew the anti-- the anti-Semitism in Poland exists, just the part where we were-- it did belong-- the part what it did belong to Poland, they were 10 million people.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were 18 and a half million Ukrainian, a million Jews, and half a million Poles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the anti-Semitism, we didn't feel over there, because-- because the-- the majority of the-- they were Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they didn't-- they didn't like the Poles.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- so we didn't-- we didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't feel it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Could you tell me a little bit how you celebrated your Jewish life, or how did you live your--",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It so happened our town was very, very active.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very active in the Zionist movement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so it was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] we-- we were-- how to say it-- we were Jewish nationalists.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were-- we-- The whole youth was organized in youth Zionist movement, because they were Betar, they were Hashomer Hatzair, Hashomer [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All those youth organization from different parties, they were in our town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many young people from our town went to-- they went in that time to Palestine as halozim, pioneers.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it so happened, my younger daughter-- my younger sister, Haya, she went-- she went to Palestine as a haluza.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I cannot recall exactly the year.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it so happened, it's destiny.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it so happened when something is destined to happen, it so-- it so happened one went away.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You could go to Israel two ways-- either as a pioneer, a haluza, or as a capitalist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A capitalist has to have $5,000 in that time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
